Mailer#show_reminder

<%= @greeting %>,

Thanks for purchasing a ticket to see <%= @user.name %> play live! The show will be on <%= @show.date %> at <%= @host.name %>'s house: 

<%= @show.address %>

The music will begin at <%= @show.time %>, so please be sure to arrive 30 minutes early. If you have any question, please contact <%= @user.name %> at <%= @show.host_em %>. 

Thanks for coming - you're in for a great night of live music!


Housed.com 
on behalf of <%= @user.name %>


